nav><\/div>\n<p><strong><i>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c cao th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e2u n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c soi c\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1. B\u1edfi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 tr\u00fang kh\u00e1 cao. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">sv368 <\/a>t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 <\/i><a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan\/\"><i>c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n <\/i><\/a><i>ngay trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/i><\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_nao_la_bat_tong_de\"><\/span><b>Th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec1 d\u1ef1a theo vi\u1ec7c t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec1 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng b\u1edfi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 tr\u00fang kh\u00e1 cao. B\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh d\u1ef1a theo t\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ebf k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i kh\u00e1c. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00f5 v\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp theo.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2061\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2061\" style=\"width: 900px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2061\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/the-nao-la-bat-tong-de-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-8.jpg\" alt=\"Th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1?\" width=\"900\" height=\"576\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/the-nao-la-bat-tong-de-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-8.jpg?v=1688375502 900w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/the-nao-la-bat-tong-de-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-8-300x192.jpg?v=1688375502 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/the-nao-la-bat-tong-de-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-8-768x492.jpg?v=1688375502 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2061\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Phan_loai_tong_de\"><\/span><b>Ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong gi\u1edbi l\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 10 lo\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1eb5n: V\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a 2 ch\u1eef s\u1ed1 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i cho ra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1eb5n. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 00, 02, 04, 20, 22\u2026<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ebb: T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1eb5n th\u00ec v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a 2 ch\u1eef s\u1ed1 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc cho ra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u1ebb. Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0: 01,03, 05, 09, 12,&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 0,1, \u2026 9: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 khi c\u1ed9ng 2 ch\u1eef s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 0 \u0111\u1ebfn 9.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Huong_dan_cach_bat_tong_de_trong_tuan_cuc_chuan\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o c\u0169ng cho t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 tr\u00fang cao. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0111\u1ec1u d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean t\u1ed5ng nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c cao th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e2u n\u0103m \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_bat_tong_de_trong_tuan_dua_theo_giai_dac_biet_ve_ngay_truoc\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a theo gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ef1c cao. Khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c trong c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ednh ra l\u1edbn h\u01a1n 10 th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 l\u1ea5y k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u1edf h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb. Nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 v\u1eeba t\u00ednh s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o d\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1 nu\u00f4i l\u00f4 trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0: sau khi t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1: 01, 02, 04, 06. Th\u00ec d\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1 nu\u00f4i trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n s\u1ebd bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 sau: 03,05, 06, 07, 08. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 t\u0103ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a theo gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1eb9o b\u1eaft l\u00f4 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea l\u00f4 gan.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2062\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2062\" style=\"width: 900px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2062\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-dua-theo-giai-dac-biet-ve-ngay-truoc-7.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a theo gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc\" width=\"900\" height=\"602\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-dua-theo-giai-dac-biet-ve-ngay-truoc-7.jpg?v=1688375502 900w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-dua-theo-giai-dac-biet-ve-ngay-truoc-7-300x201.jpg?v=1688375502 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-dua-theo-giai-dac-biet-ve-ngay-truoc-7-768x514.jpg?v=1688375502 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2062\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a theo gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_bat_tong_de_trong_tuan_theo_giai_7\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n theo gi\u1ea3i 7<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i 7, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a hai ch\u1eef s\u1ed1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd nu\u00f4i l\u00f4 trong kho\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 ng\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00ednh ra l\u1edbn h\u01a1n 10 th\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng ho\u1eb7c hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0: T\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a hai ch\u1eef s\u1ed1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai gi\u1ea3i 7 l\u00e0 5+6.= 11. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed5ng b\u1eb1ng 11 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n 10, ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a 11 l\u00e0 1+1 v\u00e0 1-1 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 2 v\u00e0 0. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, ta c\u00f3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1 l\u00e0 20 v\u00e0 02 \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i trong v\u00f2ng 2- 3 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Bat_tong_de_dua_theo_tam_giac_Pascal\"><\/span><b>B\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 d\u1ef1a theo tam gi\u00e1c Pascal<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh 1 d\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a tam gi\u00e1c. Gi\u1ea3 d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 23456 v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 78921.\u00a0 Gh\u00e9p nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh d\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1y c\u1ee7a tam gi\u00e1c l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 2-3-4-5-6-7-8-9-2-1. Ti\u1ebfp theo, d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o quy lu\u1eadt tam gi\u00e1c pascal \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed9ng 2 s\u1ed1 trong d\u00e3y g\u1ea7n nhau l\u1ea1i theo th\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 t\u1eeb tr\u00e1i qua.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u00e3y \u0111\u00e1y th\u1ee9 hai. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3: 2+3=5, 3+4=7,&#8230; 2+1=3. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e3y ti\u1ebfp th\u01b0 l\u00e0 5,7, ,,,,3. C\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 hai s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh cho ng\u00e0y sau. Ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed9ng t\u1ed5ng hai s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u00f4i khung 7 ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i l\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch soi c\u1ea7u tam gi\u00e1c. nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 hai ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c nhau ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u01b0u \u00fd n\u1eefa l\u00e0 n\u00ean lo\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng con l\u00f4 gan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao.<\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2063\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2063\" style=\"width: 900px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2063\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-tam-giac-pascal-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-6.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 d\u1ef1a theo tam gi\u00e1c pascal\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-tam-giac-pascal-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-6.jpg?v=1688375501 900w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-tam-giac-pascal-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-6-300x200.jpg?v=1688375501 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-tam-giac-pascal-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-6-768x512.jpg?v=1688375501 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2063\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 d\u1ef1a theo tam gi\u00e1c pascal<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_bat_tong_de_trong_tuan_theo_cach_tinh_nhay_coc\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n theo c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh nh\u1ea3y c\u00f3c<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngay c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u1ee7a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed9ng c\u00e1c con s\u1ed1 trong d\u00e3y s\u1ed1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t theo d\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea3y c\u00f3c. v\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 14564. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng nh\u01b0 sau: 1+5=6, 5+4=9. Ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eb7p s\u1ed1 69 v\u00e0 06 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh cho nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y sao \u0111\u00f3. <\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb b\u1ea3ng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00f4. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c<\/span><b>\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 b\u1eaft theo th\u1ee9 hai m\u1ed7i tu\u1ea7n, b\u1eaft theo b\u1ea1c nh\u1edb hay b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 theo ng\u00e0y\u2026\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2064\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2064\" style=\"width: 900px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2064\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-cach-tinh-nhay-coc-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-5.jpg\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a theo c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh nh\u1ea3y c\u00f3c\" width=\"900\" height=\"483\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-cach-tinh-nhay-coc-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-5.jpg?v=1688375500 900w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-cach-tinh-nhay-coc-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-5-300x161.jpg?v=1688375500 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/bat-tong-de-dua-theo-cach-tinh-nhay-coc-cach-bat-tong-de-trong-tuan-5-768x412.jpg?v=1688375500 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2064\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a theo c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh nh\u1ea3y c\u00f3c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 <\/span><\/i><b><i>c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 trong tu\u1ea7n <\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/span><\/i> <i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">sv368 mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n. Hy v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 tr\u00fang cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa trong b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean theo d\u00f5i sv368 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u b\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec1 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c cao th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e2u n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xa l\u1ea1 v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c soi c\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1. B\u1edfi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 tr\u00fang kh\u00e1 cao. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi ch\u01a1i l\u00f4 \u0111\u1ec1, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1eaft t\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u00e1i [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_m